h2-close-paywalls.translation:
## Đóng paywall \{#close-paywalls\}

Để thêm nút đóng paywall:

1. Trong Paywall Builder, thêm một nút và gán cho nó hành động **Close**.
2. Trong code ứng dụng, triển khai handler cho hành động `close` để đóng paywall.

```csharp showLineNumbers title="Unity"
public void PaywallViewDidPerformAction(
    AdaptyUIPaywallView view, 
    AdaptyUIUserAction action
) {
    switch (action.Type) {
        case AdaptyUIUserActionType.Close:
            view.Dismiss(null);
            break;
        default:
            // handle other events
            break;
    }
}
```

h2-open-urls-from-paywalls-pe3b0c442.translation:
```csharp showLineNumbers title="Unity"
public void PaywallViewDidPerformAction(
    AdaptyUIPaywallView view,
    AdaptyUIUserAction action
) {
    switch (action.Type) {
        case AdaptyUIUserActionType.OpenUrl:
            var urlString = action.Value;
            if(!string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(urlString)) {
                Application.OpenURL(urlString);
            }
            break;
        default:
            // handle other events
            break;
    }
}
```

h2-log-into-the-app-pe3b0c442.translation:
```csharp showLineNumbers title="Unity"
public void PaywallViewDidPerformAction(
    AdaptyUIPaywallView view,
    AdaptyUIUserAction action
) {
    switch (action.Type) {
        case AdaptyUIUserActionType.Custom:
            if (action.Value == "login") {
                // Navigate to login scene
                SceneManager.LoadScene("LoginScene");
            }
            break;
        default:
            // handle other events
            break;
    }
}
```

h2-handle-custom-actions-pe3b0c442.translation:
